<section class="content-section">
  <div class="section-heading">What is Peptide Price Lab?</div>
  <p>Peptide Price Lab is a free browser-based tool for researchers who want an apples-to-apples comparison of peptide prices. Vendors sell in different vial sizes, concentrations, and units, which makes direct price comparison nearly impossible without doing math.</p>
  <p>Peptide Price Lab does the math for you. Enter any number of products from any number of sources, and the tool instantly shows you the cost per milligram for each one, side by side. It also includes a bundle optimizer to help you hit free-shipping thresholds across multiple vendors.</p>
</section>

